lead_paragraph: Czech rider Martina Sablikova must await the outcome of an appeal to the Court of Arbitration for Sport (CAS) to see if she can compete in the Olympic women's road time trial next week after confusion about her eligibility.

headline.print_headline: Czech Sablikova Awaiting CAS Decision on Time Trial Place
